c: 34
v: 23
t: "Palibe dandaulo limene lingamveke kwa Iye kupatula lokhalo lochokera kwa iye amene walandira chilolezo chake. Mpaka pamene mantha adzachotsedwa m’mitima mwawo, iwo adzati, “Kodi ndi chiyani chimene Ambuye wanu walamulira?” Iwo adzati, “Choonadi. Ndipo Iye ndi wapamwamba ndi wamkulu.”"